HOWTO

Add a source:
  If you like to add some source then you must do the following steps.
  * package.conf (look in package.conf to get the idea)
    enter a new line with the following settings

    id  : the next free number higher then any depending
    name: name of the source package
    path: the path to the pkgsrc.sh (tree/...)
    action: the processing action for this package, none/install/uninstall

    every options needs to separate with one ';'

  * pkgsrc.sh

    copy the template to youre package path
    cp pkgsrc.sh.tpl the/path/defined/in/package/conf/pkgsrc.sh

    edit pkgsrc.sh
    every line in pkgsrc.sh have a description
